## GenericObject interface

Represents an object with an unspecific set of keys and values.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export interface GenericObject<T = any> 
```

## Remarks

You can enforce the type of all values in the object by passing a type instead of using the default `any`<!-- -->.
